{"tid":1799191,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"（揾game) PS1 競速動作遊戲，渣著架電單車向前衝打敵人，可同電單車合體變機械人","createTime":"2019-12-26T18:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T04:43:25.000Z","uid":266172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b3855629ca4c0b2c0d1e09987f5d4c90e0f46605","tid":1799191,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:33:22.000Z","msg":"（揾game) PS1 競速動作遊戲。<br />\n每一關都會渣著架電單車向前行，而中途會有敵人打，而渣電單車個人可以隨時同電單車合體變機械人再作戰，而好似成日都有大佬打的。<br />\n其實唔算賽車game，但我冇記錯有限時，要完時間前去到終點（可能記錯）。<br />\n<br />\n可以簡三個個主角，紅，白，黑。<br />\n紅色用拳，白色用槍，黑色用光劍。<br />\n三個主角條路線故事都有少少唔同。<br />\n<br />\n我記得用黑色的故事，黑色係條team的leader，去到半路出賣鐘意佢的白色妹妹，好似殺左佢，之後個紅色揾黑色報仇。<br />\n感謝。"},{"pid":"c8010ecddc369c30ae4eb32050200d86fcd23196","tid":1799191,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T18:34:00.000Z","msg":"日本game來"},{"pid":"28d6762464ea6d395a2c975926319977e94f8695","tid":1799191,"uid":18241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T21:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YtY5S3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YtY5S3.jpg&h=9a8ff48e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fb6b4fe6edf3358a944ddc7d8fc72ec072f7588","tid":1799191,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28d6762464ea6d395a2c975926319977e94f8695","tid":1799191,"uid":18241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T21:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YtY5S3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YtY5S3.jpg&h=9a8ff48e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"thanks!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.g